The remains of Senator Buruju Kashamu, have been buried at his Ijebu-Igbo country home. The Nation reports he was buried at around 12:55 pm on Sunday. Ogun Governor Dapo Abiodun was part of the crowd that bidded the politician a tearful farewell. Sympathisers shunned COVID-19 protocols during the burial with many of them struggling to have a good view of the funeral activities. Kashamu died at 62 on Saturday of COVID-19 complications. Details shortlyâ€¦